<br>
Feature of the game = anything(aka Z-axis), be it a known bug or glitch in the game (aka warping mobs &amp; bad pathing), that makes it harder to kill/do anything or anymob<br>
<br>
<br>
Unfortunatly for the players there are so many exploits/features that SOE &amp; VI either refuse to fix, or nerf the mob into non-existance, the game can quickly become uninteresting. <p><div align="center">
